headline: Conagra Tests Protein Heavy Breakfast Bowls As Frozen Strategy Indicator
summary: Conagra Brands, traded as NYSE:CAG, has introduced Banquet MEGA Breakfast Bowls to its frozen breakfast lineup. The new products feature high protein recipes and use a tray in tray steaming method to cook components inside the microwave. This launch extends the Banquet MEGA brand from dinners into breakfast, targeting shoppers looking for convenient, filling options at home. headline: BANQUET® MEGA™ BREAKFAST BOWLS DELIVER BIG PROTEIN FOR YOUR MORNING
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE: CAG), one of North America's leading branded food companies, is bringing a protein-packed new offering to breakfast with the debut of new Banquet® MEGA™ Breakfast Bowls. With 30g of protein per bowl, four new varieties offer a hearty, tasty breakfast that's built on the Banquet MEGA promise of big flavor, big protein, and big value1.
